Could not find any path to a clock for precharge or latch '%s'\n
err.doc: This message indicates that there is no path from a defined clock to the actual command. This generaly means that a clock declaration is missing for the circuit. Often, missing clocks are clocks that are generated from the interface clock into a latch node. This latch node might be the one to also set as a clock.
